//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0005>"Sayaka-chan..."
<enT0005>"Sayaka-chan..."

//TEXT
<jaT0006>I felt powerless and hopeless. I wasn't able to support her at all. She probably couldn't even hear me over her tears.
<enT0006>I felt powerless and hopeless. I wasn't able to support her at all. She probably couldn't even hear me over her tears.

//TEXT 【Sayaka】
<jaT0007>"*Sob*...Aya, Aya..."
<enT0007>"*Sob*...Aya, Aya..."

//TEXT
<jaT0008>Our maintenance pod lost control and continued to fly straight. Soon enough, the Hamal will find us.
